with its slight floral notes and high acidity, this light bodied white is perfect for a hot summer day or a cool autumn night. it's absolutely gorgeous and a wine i could and have drank on all occasions! - courtney reds caroline morey, le chainey, santenay 2017 - $95 'this is the bottle that you need if you're looking for a great red burgundy that is really enjoyable for a reasonable price. the palate is bright and luscious. its red fruit aromas, flowers, spices and herbs will surround your olfactory senses' - 'hayzen chateau lafon-rochet saint-estephe 4eme cru 2010 - $150 'a full-bodied bordeaux drinking beautifully right now!
